Nick, is a young Scottish soccer player living in the big city. 
He meets Karen, and the two fall in love and move in together. 
Soon after, Nick exhibits signs of a serious illness. As his 
body slowly succumbs to Multiple Sclerosis, he experiences 
a wide sweep of jagged emotions, and in the process gives 
himself and those who love him the strength to carry on.
